        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Rural Outdoor Investment Act</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Commerce to make grants to eligible recipients for outdoor recreation projects to spur economic development, with a focus on rural communities.</p> <p>Commerce shall develop a partnership agreement to provide for the development of, among other things, basic training, including in-person or modular training sessions, for small businesses and rural communities.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
